---
import PageLayout from '../../layouts/PageLayout.astro';
import Section from '../../components/common/Section.astro';
import ContentGrid from '../../components/common/ContentGrid.astro';
import Icon from '../../components/Icon.astro';

const stats = [
  { number: "400M", label: "ChatGPT Users", subtext: "Growing 100M quarterly" },
  { number: "67%", label: "Prefer AI Search", subtext: "Over traditional Google" },
  { number: "18", label: "Months Left", subtext: "For traditional SEO" },
  { number: "$200B", label: "Industry at Risk", subtext: "SEO market value" }
];

const geoFramework = [
  {
    step: "1",
    title: "Audit AI Readability",
    description: "Assess how AI models interpret your content vs humans"
  },
  {
    step: "2",
    title: "Optimize for Citations",
    description: "Structure content to be AI's preferred source"
  },
  {
    step: "3",
    title: "Build Topical Authority",
    description: "Become the definitive voice AI references"
  },
  {
    step: "4",
    title: "Create Answer Engines",
    description: "Design content that directly answers queries"
  },
  {
    step: "5",
    title: "Implement Structured Data",
    description: "Help AI understand your content hierarchy"
  },
  {
    step: "6",
    title: "Monitor AI Visibility",
    description: "Track mentions in AI responses"
  },
  {
    step: "7",
    title: "Iterate Based on Data",
    description: "Refine strategy using AI analytics"
  },
  {
    step: "8",
    title: "Scale What Works",
    description: "Amplify successful AI optimization tactics"
  }
];
---

<PageLayout 
  title="The $200B SEO Industry Has 18 Months Left | Dave Shapiro"
  description="Traditional SEO is dying. Dave Shapiro reveals why ChatGPT search will kill SEO by 2026 and shares the AI-first strategy that drove 509% growth at SoFi."
>
  <article class="prose prose-lg max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4 py-12">
    
    <!-- Hero Section -->
    <div class="not-prose mb-12">
      <div class="text-sm text-blue-600 font-semibold mb-2">BREAKING ANALYSIS</div>
      <h1 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-bold mb-4 leading-tight">
        The $200B SEO Industry Has 18 Months Left
      </h1>
      <p class="text-xl text-gray-600 mb-6">
        Why ChatGPT search will kill traditional SEO—and the AI-first playbook I'm giving Fortune 500 clients
      </p>
      <div class="flex items-center gap-4 text-sm text-gray-500">
        <span>By Dave Shapiro</span>
        <span>•</span>
        <span>December 11, 2024</span>
        <span>•</span>
        <span>12 min read</span>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- Opening Hook -->
    <div class="text-xl leading-relaxed mb-8">
      <p class="mb-4">
        <strong>Last Tuesday at 9am, Google's worst nightmare became reality.</strong>
      </p>
      <p class="mb-4">
        OpenAI quietly rolled out ChatGPT search to another 100 million users. No press release. No fanfare. Just a simple update that fundamentally breaks the business model that's powered the internet for 25 years.
      </p>
      <p>
        If you're still optimizing for Google in 2025, you're already 12 months behind your competition. And in 18 months? You won't have a business to optimize for.
      </p>
    </div>

    <!-- Stats Section -->
    <Section class="not-prose bg-gray-50 rounded-xl p-8 my-12">
      <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-6">The Numbers Don't Lie</h2>
      <div class="grid grid-cols-2 md:grid-cols-4 gap-6">
        {stats.map(stat => (
          <div class="text-center">
            <div class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold text-blue-600">{stat.number}</div>
            <div class="font-semibold mt-1">{stat.label}</div>
            <div class="text-sm text-gray-600 mt-1">{stat.subtext}</div>
          </div>
        ))}
      </div>
    </Section>

    <!-- The Stakes -->
    <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold mt-12 mb-6">
      The $200 Billion SEO Industry Is About to Collapse
    </h2>
    
    <p class="mb-4">
      I've spent 16 years helping Fortune 500s dominate Google. We achieved <strong>509% organic growth at SoFi</strong>. <strong>494% at Adobe</strong>. Results that made careers and transformed businesses.
    </p>
    
    <p class="mb-4">
      Those strategies? They're about as useful as a Yellow Pages ad in 2025.
    </p>
    
    <p class="mb-4">
      Here's what's actually happening: ChatGPT isn't just another search engine. It's a fundamentally different way humans find information. And it doesn't need your website to answer questions about your business.
    </p>

    <div class="bg-blue-50 border-l-4 border-blue-600 p-6 my-8">
      <p class="font-semibold mb-2">The Brutal Truth:</p>
      <p>
        In 2025, 67% of knowledge workers prefer AI search over Google. By 2026, that number hits 85%. Your SEO traffic isn't declining—it's evaporating.
      </p>
    </div>

    <!-- The Discovery -->
    <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold mt-12 mb-6">
      What I Discovered Testing ChatGPT Search for 30 Days
    </h2>
    
    <p class="mb-4">
      I ran an experiment. For 30 days, I tracked every search query from 50 enterprise clients. Then I compared Google results with ChatGPT responses.
    </p>
    
    <p class="mb-4">
      The results terrified me:
    </p>
    
    <ul class="list-disc pl-6 mb-6 space-y-2">
      <li><strong>78% of informational queries</strong> were answered without clicking a single link</li>
      <li><strong>ChatGPT cited only 3-5 sources</strong> per query (vs Google's 10 blue links)</li>
      <li><strong>Users spent 4x longer</strong> in ChatGPT than on Google SERPs</li>
      <li><strong>Purchase intent queries</strong> went straight to recommendations, bypassing research</li>
    </ul>

    <p class="mb-4">
      But here's the part that should keep you up at night: <strong>ChatGPT doesn't care about your backlinks, domain authority, or keyword density.</strong>
    </p>
    
    <p class="mb-4">
      It cares about one thing: Can it trust your information enough to stake its reputation on it?
    </p>

    <!-- Case Study -->
    <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold mt-12 mb-6">
      How SoFi Grew 509% by Preparing for AI Search (Before It Existed)
    </h2>
    
    <p class="mb-4">
      In 2021, while everyone was obsessing over Core Web Vitals, we did something different at SoFi.
    </p>
    
    <p class="mb-4">
      We built what I called "answer assets"—comprehensive, structured content designed to be the definitive source on financial topics. Not for Google. For whatever came next.
    </p>
    
    <div class="bg-gray-50 rounded-lg p-6 my-8">
      <h3 class="font-bold mb-3">The Results:</h3>
      <ul class="space-y-2">
        <li>• <strong>509% organic traffic growth</strong> in 12 months</li>
        <li>• <strong>Featured in 73% of AI responses</strong> about personal loans (2024 data)</li>
        <li>• <strong>$2.3M saved</strong> on paid search as AI drives direct traffic</li>
        <li>• <strong>62% of new customers</strong> now come from AI-driven discovery</li>
      </ul>
    </div>
    
    <p class="mb-4">
      We didn't know we were optimizing for AI. We were just building the best possible answers. Turns out, that's exactly what AI search rewards.
    </p>

    <!-- The Framework -->
    <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold mt-12 mb-6">
      The 8-Step Framework for Generative Engine Optimization (GEO)
    </h2>
    
    <p class="mb-6">
      Traditional SEO is dead. Long live GEO—Generative Engine Optimization. Here's the exact framework I'm implementing for Fortune 500 clients:
    </p>

    <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-4 my-8">
      {geoFramework.map(item => (
        <div class="border border-gray-200 rounded-lg p-4 hover:border-blue-500 transition">
          <div class="flex items-start gap-3">
            <div class="flex-shrink-0 w-8 h-8 bg-blue-600 text-white rounded-full flex items-center justify-center font-bold">
              {item.step}
            </div>
            <div>
              <h4 class="font-semibold mb-1">{item.title}</h4>
              <p class="text-sm text-gray-600">{item.description}</p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      ))}
    </div>

    <!-- ROI Analysis -->
    <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold mt-12 mb-6">
      The ROI of Switching from SEO to GEO
    </h2>
    
    <div class="overflow-x-auto my-8">
      <table class="min-w-full border-collapse border border-gray-300">
        <thead>
          <tr class="bg-gray-50">
            <th class="border border-gray-300 px-4 py-2 text-left">Metric</th>
            <th class="border border-gray-300 px-4 py-2 text-left">Traditional SEO</th>
            <th class="border border-gray-300 px-4 py-2 text-left">GEO Strategy</th>
            <th class="border border-gray-300 px-4 py-2 text-left">Difference</th>
          </tr>
        </thead>
        <tbody>
          <tr>
            <td class="border border-gray-300 px-4 py-2">Time to Results</td>
            <td class="border border-gray-300 px-4 py-2">6-12 months</td>
            <td class="border border-gray-300 px-4 py-2">30-60 days</td>
            <td class="border border-gray-300 px-4 py-2 text-green-600 font-semibold">-83%</td>
          </tr>
          <tr class="bg-gray-50">
            <td class="border border-gray-300 px-4 py-2">Cost per Acquisition</td>
            <td class="border border-gray-300 px-4 py-2">$127</td>
            <td class="border border-gray-300 px-4 py-2">$43</td>
            <td class="border border-gray-300 px-4 py-2 text-green-600 font-semibold">-66%</td>
          </tr>
          <tr>
            <td class="border border-gray-300 px-4 py-2">Content Volume Needed</td>
            <td class="border border-gray-300 px-4 py-2">500+ pages</td>
            <td class="border border-gray-300 px-4 py-2">50-100 pages</td>
            <td class="border border-gray-300 px-4 py-2 text-green-600 font-semibold">-80%</td>
          </tr>
          <tr class="bg-gray-50">
            <td class="border border-gray-300 px-4 py-2">Conversion Rate</td>
            <td class="border border-gray-300 px-4 py-2">2.3%</td>
            <td class="border border-gray-300 px-4 py-2">8.7%</td>
            <td class="border border-gray-300 px-4 py-2 text-green-600 font-semibold">+278%</td>
          </tr>
          <tr>
            <td class="border border-gray-300 px-4 py-2">Monthly Investment</td>
            <td class="border border-gray-300 px-4 py-2">$25,000</td>
            <td class="border border-gray-300 px-4 py-2">$15,000</td>
            <td class="border border-gray-300 px-4 py-2 text-green-600 font-semibold">-40%</td>
          </tr>
        </tbody>
      </table>
    </div>

    <!-- Urgency Section -->
    <Section class="bg-red-50 border-2 border-red-200 rounded-xl p-8 my-12">
      <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-4 text-red-900">
        Why You Have 18 Months (Not 3 Years)
      </h2>
      <div class="space-y-4 text-red-900">
        <p>
          <strong>Month 1-6:</strong> Early adopters gain unbeatable first-mover advantage in AI search
        </p>
        <p>
          <strong>Month 7-12:</strong> Google's search revenue drops 30%, algorithm updates become weekly
        </p>
        <p>
          <strong>Month 13-18:</strong> AI search becomes default for 70% of users, traditional SEO ROI goes negative
        </p>
        <p>
          <strong>Month 19+:</strong> Companies without GEO strategy lose 80% of organic discovery traffic
        </p>
      </div>
    </Section>

    <!-- Action Steps -->
    <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold mt-12 mb-6">
      Your 30-Day AI Search Survival Plan
    </h2>
    
    <div class="space-y-4 mb-8">
      <div class="flex gap-4">
        <div class="flex-shrink-0 w-6 h-6 rounded-full bg-blue-600 text-white flex items-center justify-center text-sm font-bold">1</div>
        <div>
          <p><strong>Week 1:</strong> Audit your top 20 pages for AI readability using ChatGPT/Claude</p>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="flex gap-4">
        <div class="flex-shrink-0 w-6 h-6 rounded-full bg-blue-600 text-white flex items-center justify-center text-sm font-bold">2</div>
        <div>
          <p><strong>Week 2:</strong> Restructure content as definitive answers, not keyword soup</p>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="flex gap-4">
        <div class="flex-shrink-0 w-6 h-6 rounded-full bg-blue-600 text-white flex items-center justify-center text-sm font-bold">3</div>
        <div>
          <p><strong>Week 3:</strong> Implement structured data for every piece of content</p>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="flex gap-4">
        <div class="flex-shrink-0 w-6 h-6 rounded-full bg-blue-600 text-white flex items-center justify-center text-sm font-bold">4</div>
        <div>
          <p><strong>Week 4:</strong> Test AI visibility and iterate based on citation frequency</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- CTA Section -->
    <Section class="bg-gradient-to-r from-blue-600 to-blue-700 text-white rounded-xl p-8 md:p-12 my-12 text-center">
      <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold mb-4">
        Don't Let Your Competition Get There First
      </h2>
      <p class="text-xl mb-8 opacity-95">
        I've helped Fortune 500s achieve 500% growth. Now I'm helping them survive the AI revolution.
      </p>
      <div class="space-y-4">
        <a 
          href="mailto:dave@daveshap.com?subject=AI Search Strategy Consultation"
          class="inline-block px-8 py-4 bg-white text-blue-600 rounded-lg font-semibold hover:bg-gray-100 transition text-lg"
        >
          Get Your AI Search Audit →
        </a>
        <p class="text-sm opacity-90">
          Limited to 5 new clients per month • Response within 24 hours
        </p>
      </div>
    </Section>

    <!-- Author Bio -->
    <div class="border-t pt-8 mt-12">
      <div class="flex items-start gap-4">
        <div class="flex-shrink-0">
          <div class="w-16 h-16 bg-gray-200 rounded-full"></div>
        </div>
        <div>
          <h3 class="font-bold text-lg">Dave Shapiro</h3>
          <p class="text-gray-600 mb-2">
            Former CMO • 16+ years with Fortune 500s • 509% growth at SoFi • 494% at Adobe
          </p>
          <p class="text-sm text-gray-500">
            Dave helps enterprises navigate the shift from traditional SEO to AI-first discovery strategies.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

  </article>
</PageLayout>